replies.bodyText:
One thing that is nasty about database migrations is that if failed, the user is left with app that is disfunctional, potentially leading to a data loss.
If we throw a well defined exception here, we can catch that in ShowErrorActivity and propose a workaround of downgrading the app to previous version.
@tobiasKaminsky Worth pursuing from UX point of view?
